		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The 'VERY VERY rare' NES2 boards also have the same multi-out port as the SFC/SNES/N64. I'm pretty sure I've narrowed down the specific source of interference and exactly where its path brings it to cause the lines. As I said, when I'm positive, I'll post about it in detail.
<br />
<br />The lines shouldn't exist on a RetroDuo; but they have to come from the same source, else they wouldn't look the same.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


